                        </div>
                        
                        <h4 style="margin: 2rem 0 1rem 0; color: #0c323f;">Paquetes empresariales:</h4>
                        
                        <div class="features-grid">
                            <div class="feature-item">
                                <div class="feature-title">🚀 Startup</div>
                                <div class="feature-description">297€* | Setup + 3 meses mantenimiento</div>
